T01TD1165E:237b-1: sapta ta th'a ga ta sto tra:/
T01TD1165E:237b-3: de bzhin gshegs pa bdun gyi bstod pa //
T01TD1165E:237b-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1165E:237b-5: 'gro ba'i bla ma lha mi 'jig rten phyir mchod cing //
T01TD1165E:237b-6: thugs rjes gsal zhing gzhan la phan pa'i thar pa ston //
T01TD1165E:237b-7: srid gsum chu chen mthar phyin bde 'gror son pa po //
T01TD1165E:237b-8: de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par gzigs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1165E:237b-9: srid pa'i rgya mtsho mtha' dang pha rol med pa 'di //
T01TD1165E:237b-10: 'jig rten nub cing 'dug pa rab tu gzigs nas kyang //
T01TD1165E:237b-11: phan gdags phyir ni chos rnams ston pa gang yin pa //
T01TD1165E:237b-12: rgyal ba gtsug tor mnga' ba de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1165E:237b-13: nyi zla dag las 'das pa'i gzi brjid mnga' ba des //
T01TD1165E:237b-14: ye shes dang ni spyod pa'i ngang tshul rnams las kyang //
T01TD1165E:238a-0: rgya mtsho'i 'jing ltar gting dpag nus par @238a * //
T01TD1165E:238a-2: sangs rgyas thams cad skyob pa de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1165E:238a-3: gang gi grags pa zla ba'i 'od zer 'dra ba yis //
T01TD1165E:238a-4: sa stengs mtha' dag rab tu brgyan par snang ba dang //
T01TD1165E:238a-5: au du mb'a ra'i me tog bzhin du rmad byung ba //
T01TD1165E:238a-6: thub dbang chen po log dang sel la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1165E:238a-7: dri ma med cing rtag tu phan par mdzad pa dang //
T01TD1165E:238a-8: chags pa med pa gang gi dri ma med pa'i thugs //
T01TD1165E:238a-9: rnam par 'phro bas mun pa'i thibs po rab bcom zhing //
T01TD1165E:238a-10: lha yis mchod pa'i gser thub de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1165E:238a-11: btso ma'i gser gyi phung po'i kha dog 'dra ba yi ;
T01TD1165E:238a-12: / gzi brjid 'bar ba nyi ma stong pas lhag pa mnga' //
T01TD1165E:238a-13: skyi bo kun gyis phyag byas 'jig rten mchog gyur pa //
T01TD1165E:238a-14: 'od srungs mtshan gsol gang yin de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1165E:238a-15: nyi ma'i 'od zer mang pos pad+ma'i tshal phye ltar //
T01TD1165E:238a-16: gsung gi 'od zer mang pos 'jig rten sad par mdzad //
T01TD1165E:238a-17: ston pa sh'akya thub pa thugs rje sgron ma can //
T01TD1165E:238a-18: mya ngan 'das ston gang yin de la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1165E:238a-19: gang gi byang chub skye ba gcig gis thogs gyur cing //
T01TD1165E:238a-20: byams pa zhes bya dga' ldan gnam gyi gnas na bzhugs //
T01TD1165E:238a-21: sa stengs bde bar gshegs par 'gyur ba gang yin pa //
T01TD1165E:238a-22: de la bdag ni rtag tu dad pas phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1165E:238a-23: 'das pa'i rgyal ba bdun po dang ni phyis gshegs pa //
T01TD1165E:238a-24: brgyad pa byang chub sems dpa' bdag gis bstod pa yis //
T01TD1165E:238a-25: bsod nams mtha' yas dpag med bdag gis gang thob pa //
T01TD1165E:238a-26: des ni sems can rnams kyang skyon dang bral gyur cig / de bzhin gshegs pa bdun gyi bstod pa rdzogs so /
T01TD1165E:238a-28: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po pad+ma ka ra wa rma dang /
T01TD1165E:238a-29: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba dge slong rin chen bzang pos bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa//
